<TEXT>
<P>
I enjoyed reading "O, Happy Days!" The cover, showing a neighborhood in Sherman 
Oaks in 1957, was particularly interesting. Only one thing was missing -- a 
picture of that same street as it looks 33 years later. 
</P>
<P>
WM. R. SMITH 
</P>
<P>
Oceanside 
</P>
