lectures on how TV uses violence to "grab an audience." ; Photo, Brian 
Stonehill's class at the Claremont School of Theology is told that viewers 
should be alert to nuances. LOU MACK / Los Angeles Times; Photo, BRIAN 
STONEHILL: professor, Pomona College 
</P>
