<HEADLINE>
<P>
COLLEGE NEWS: CAL STATE L.A. TEAM WINS COLLEGE BOWL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Cal State L.A. has been awarded the Ann Reynolds Cup after placing first among 
California State University College Bowl teams in the Assn. of College 
Unions-International Region 15 College Bowl Match. 
</P>
<P>
Students Robin Creason, Steve Pencall, Waheed Boctor and Mat Gleason competed 
with teams from 18 universities in California, Arizona and Hawaii. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032590-0024 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 194484 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 25, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
San Gabriel Valley; Part J; Page 7; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
