'DECLARATION' CAUSES OUTPOURING OF DEEPLY DIVIDED OPINIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Gosh, your lesbian piece was really on key and wonderfully done. 
</P>
<P>
You also managed to cram into the back part of the article a bunch of good info 
on us male gays and the lesbian/gay situation in general. 
</P>
<P>
Truly, the "New Gays," as I tend to call the kids in their teens and 20s who 
are coming out these days (I'm 44), seem to come out more easily and into a 
space we made for them. As a result, their personalities look more 
straightforward because they have spent less time hiding from any part of life. 
</P>
<P>
JAMES BAKER 
