had expected to rebuild the defensive line around him this year. 
</P>
<P>
On the last play of the scrimmage, watched by about 3,000, freshman quarterback 
Reggie Perry suffered a dislocated left elbow. Perry, a 6-foot-2, 195-pound 
athlete from Denison, Tex., reminds Smith of Rodney Peete because of his 
running style. MAL FLORENCE 
