</P>
<P>
"The Guns of Navarone" -- 1961 
</P>
<P>
"Barabbas" -- 1962 
</P>
<P>
"Lawrence of Arabia" -- 1962 
</P>
<P>
"Requiem for a Heavyweight" B&amp;W -- 1962 
</P>
<P>
"Behold a Pale Horse" -- 1963 
</P>
<P>
"Zorba the Greek" B&amp;W -- 1963 
</P>
<P>
"Lost Command" -- 1966 
</P>
<P>
"Shoes of the Fisherman" -- 1968 
</P>
<P>
"A Dream of Kings" -- 1969 
</P>
<P>
