</P>
<P>
Background: Antos worked as a Seal Beach planner from 1972-83 and served on 
several county committees. He ran for the District 1 seat four years ago, 
losing to Mayor Victor S. Grgas. 
</P>
<P>
James Cook 
</P>
<P>
Age: 37 
</P>
