Hospital Auxiliary in Long Beach and was a founding member of the Long Beach 
chapter of GOP Juniors. She also was given an honorary lifetime membership to 
the Long Beach Parents-Teachers Assn. 
</P>
<P>
Douglas Hoxeng 
</P>
<P>
